HEADWORD: Dezincification
<hw>De*zinc`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act
or process of freeing from zinc; also, the condition resulting from the
removal of zinc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

